data.description: Take a look at this immaculate ranch styled home with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and situated on a very nice lot outside the city limits!!  This home features a very large living room, kitchen/dining combo, laundry room, two nice size bedrooms, with a huge master suite with a walk-in closet and private bathroom!!  In addition this home has a 1 car garage, nice sized front porch and fully enclosed back porch. This is one you don't want to miss, so make your appoitment today before it is too late!!  Seller is also willing to leave the home fully furnished!!
